@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_iruwpx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.15 - v2 + 0.07)) + wp.sin((v0 + 0.73 * v1 + 0.87)))
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.abs(v0 + 0.97) - (v0 + 0.04 / v1 + 0.97)))
    v2 = 0.69
    v0 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.08 + v0 + 0.39)) * ((v1 + 0.89 * tmp + 0.89) / wp.abs(v1 + 1.00)))
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.exp(v2 + 0.87)))
    v1 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
